metadata.name: Reach
metadata.description:
「Reach」
For a better future

For god's sake, yes I know this world we live in is limiting fate is supreme. 
There's no room for dreams
I'm sick of its scheme but hey this is me!
Shooting pass today, I may be crazy running towards nothing real, an Ideal I believe.
Nothing can stop me, just look at me go!

- Daydream Skytrain, Orangestar
